ankeleiqi_1_1.value: Every fairy tale needs a lovely princess.

ankeleiqi_1_2.value: It's your own fairy tale world!

ankeleiqi_1_2_1.value: I want... Teacher in my fairy tale too please!

ankeleiqi_2.value: Anchorage wants to draw... what I dreamed of above the clouds

ankeleiqi_2_1_1.value: Teacher and me holding hands eating candy... So soft

ankeleiqi_2_2_1.value: Pretty... On top of the clouds with Teacher and happy

nengdai_1.value: Are you the only one who can see this?

nengdai_1_1_1.value: Good. Then I will share my daily activities with you from now on. I just hope it doesn't bore you...

nengdai_1_2.value: I'm happy to have something so lovely all to myself.

nengdai_1_2_1.value: Really... If you came over every day, you could have even more, don't you think?

tianlangxing_1.value: Maids live to satisfy their masters, so I have taken the liberty of learning new skills for the sake of better serving my honourable Master.

tianlangxing_1_1.value: I hope I can satisfy you, too, Sirius.

tianlangxing_1_1_1.value: Do you really mean that, Master? Then please allow me to use all that I've learned to serve you!

tianlangxing_1_2_1.value: Yes! Very useful ones that will help bind us together forever!

xinzexi_1.value: Bleeeck! I drank something really bitter. I knew I was wrong to try new things!

xinzexi_1_1.value: Are you okay? What could possibly be that bad?

xinzexi_1_1_1.value: Of course I'm not. It's so bitter, I'm gonna DIE! You need to nurse me back to health, honey!

xinzexi_1_2.value: What kind of medicine can cure that bitterness?

xinzexi_1_2_1.value: I know just the thing! The fruit juice YOU bring me. One sip will wash away all the bitterness!

xinzexi_2.value: I wanna do something for you, honey~ Got any ideas?

xinzexi_2_1.value: How about something you want to do?

xinzexi_2_1_1.value: Hmm... I've already done everything I want, and I'm spending time with YOU!

xinzexi_2_2.value: I'm happy as long as you're with me.

xinzexi_2_2_1.value: That's not enough at all! We gotta do something more meaningful, more exciting! Like... How about a couple's vacation?
